Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 05 of Feet MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Ligamenta' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Ankle joint' radio button is enabled
And 'Tear of the spring ligament complex' radio button is enabled
And 'Lesion of the tarsal sinus' radio button is enabled
And 'Bifurcate ligament' radio button is enabled
And 'Tear of the plantar ligament' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Ankle joint' radio button
Then 'Rupture of the tibiofibular syndesmosis' radio button is enabled
And 'Rupture of lateral ligament of the ankle' radio button is enabled
And 'Rupture of medial ligament of the ankle' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Rupture of the tibiofibular syndesmosis' radio button
Then 'Lig. tibiofibular anterior (anterior syndesmosis)' checkbox is enabled
And 'Posterior tibiofibular ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Interosseous tibiofibular ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Acute' radio button is enabled
And 'Chronic' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Rupture of the tibiofibular syndesmosis' checkbox
Then 'Partial tear' radio button is enabled
And 'Complete tear' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Posterior tibiofibular ligament' checkbox
Then 'Tertius fracture' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Acute' radio button
Then 'Soft tissue hematoma' checkbox is enabled


When I select 'Rupture of lateral ligament of the ankle' radio button
Then 'Anterior talofibular ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Calcaneofibular ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Posterior talofibular ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Acute' radio button is enabled
And 'Chronic' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Anterior talofibular ligament' checkbox
Then 'Partial tear' radio button is enabled
And 'Complete tear' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Acute' radio button
Then 'Soft tissue hematoma' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Chronic' radio button
Then 'Scar tissue' checkbox is enabled


When I select 'Rupture of medial ligament of the ankle' radio button
Then 'Tibionavicular ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tibiocalcaneal ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Anterior tibiotalar ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Posterior tibiotalar ligament' checkbox is enabled
And 'Acute' radio button is enabled
And 'Chronic' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Tibionavicular ligament' checkbox
Then 'Avulsion fracture of the medial malleolus' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Tibiocalcaneal ligament' checkbox
Then 'Avulsion fracture of the medial malleolus' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Acute' radio button
Then 'Soft tissue hematoma' checkbox is enabled
